HEADWORD: Ginkgopsida
<hw>Ginkgopsida</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
division of trees comprising the ginkgos. In some systems it is
classified as a class (<class>Ginkgopsida</class>) and in others as a
subdivision (Ginkgophytina or <phylum>Ginkgophyta</phylum>); used in
some classifications for one of five subdivisions of
Gymnospermophyta.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Ginkgopsida, class <class>Ginkgopsida</class>,
subdivision Ginkgophytina.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

